'''牛肉牛乳因子'''（{{lang-en|bovine meat and milk factors}}，簡稱BMMF）是在{{Citation needed|陆生哺乳动物<ref>包含常见的猪肉、黄牛肉、羊肉、马肉。</ref><ref name=Falida2019 />的|time=2021-03-22T23:09:27+00:00}}肉和奶中常见的环状[[DNA|DNA]]，和[[結腸癌|結腸癌]]或[[乳腺癌|乳腺癌]]的形成有關<ref>{{Cite web|title=Episomal-Persistent DNA in Cancer- and Chronic Diseases|url=https://www.dkfz.de/en/episomal-persistierende-DNA/groups/Research.html|url-status=no|access-date=2021-03-03|website=Deutsches Krebsforschungszentrum|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316182446/https://www.dkfz.de/en/episomal-persistierende-DNA/groups/Research.html}}</ref>。

== 潜在来源 ==
細菌體內的[[质粒|质粒]]是一種[[复制子|复制子]]，類似於被整合入細菌體內的共生病毒。[[不动杆菌|不动杆菌]]是一類廣泛存在於土壤中的細菌，可被牛隻攝入，[[鲍曼不动杆菌|鲍曼不动杆菌]]被發現存在於21.1%的德國乳用牛種及6.8%的肉用牛種中<ref>Seasonal Occurrence and Carbapenem Susceptibility of Bovine Acinetobacter baumannii in Germany</ref>，其质粒DNA爲環狀。牛肉牛乳因子作爲一類環狀DNA，與這種质粒DNA具有相似性<ref name="Hausen-dVilliers-etc2021" />，與[[矮化病毒科|矮化病毒科]]、[[双生病毒科|双生病毒科]]等[[單鏈DNA病毒|單鏈DNA病毒]]的DNA亦具相似性。<ref name="Hausen-dVilliers-etal2019" />
== 人体内作用机理 ==
牛肉牛乳因子和癌症的潛在關係是由在[[海德堡大学|海德堡大学]]{{link-de|德国癌症研究中心|Deutsches Krebsforschungszentrum}}工作的[[哈拉尔德·楚尔·豪森|哈拉尔德·楚尔·豪森]]和Ethel-Michele de Villiers，其基礎是以流行病學資料的評估<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Hausen|first=Harald zur|last2=Villiers|first2=Ethel-Michele de|date=2015|title=Dairy cattle serum and milk factors contributing to the risk of colon and breast cancers|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1002/ijc.29466|journal=International Journal of Cancer|language=en|volume=137|issue=4|pages=959–967|doi=10.1002/ijc.29466|issn=1097-0215}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last=Hausen|first=Harald zur|last2=Bund|first2=Timo|last3=Villiers|first3=Ethel-Michele de|date=2019|title=Specific nutritional infections early in life as risk factors for human colon and breast cancers several decades later|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1002/ijc.31882|journal=International Journal of Cancer|language=en|volume=144|issue=7|pages=1574–1583|doi=10.1002/ijc.31882|issn=1097-0215|access-date=2021-03-22|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604160101/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1002/ijc.31882|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Däuble|first=Wolfgang|title=Nobelpreisträger zur Hausen: Warum haben Inder so selten Darmkrebs?|language=de|trans-title=Nobel laureate zur Hausen: Why do Indians so rarely have colon cancer?|work=FAZ.NET|url=https://www.faz.net/1.2904246|url-status=live|access-date=2021-03-03|issn=0174-4909}}</ref>以及人類血清白蛋白抗體的探討<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|last=Eilebrecht|first=Sebastian|last2=Hotz-Wagenblatt|first2=Agnes|last3=Sarachaga|first3=Victor|last4=Burk|first4=Amelie|last5=Falida|first5=Konstantina|last6=Chakraborty|first6=Deblina|last7=Nikitina|first7=Ekaterina|last8=Tessmer|first8=Claudia|last9=Whitley|first9=Corinna|last10=Sauerland|first10=Charlotte|last11=Gunst|first11=Karin|date=2018-02-12|title=Expression and replication of virus-like circular DNA in human cells|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-018-21317-w|journal=Scientific Reports|language=en|volume=8|issue=1|pages=2851|doi=10.1038/s41598-018-21317-w|issn=2045-2322|doi-access=free|access-date=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316182301/https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-018-21317-w|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Erhöhtes Krebsrisiko durch Kuhmilch und Rindfleisch?|trans-title=Increased cancer risk from cow's milk and beef?|url=https://www.aerztezeitung.de/Medizin/Erhoehtes-Krebsrisiko-durch-Kuhmilch-und-Rindfleisch-224843.html|url-status=no|access-date=2021-03-03|website=AerzteZeitung.de|language=de|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127141504/https://www.aerztezeitung.de/Medizin/Erhoehtes-Krebsrisiko-durch-Kuhmilch-und-Rindfleisch-224843.html}}</ref>為基礎。研究也指出牛肉牛乳因子和[[神經退化障礙|神經退化障礙]]（例如[[多发性硬化症|多发性硬化症]]）有潛在關係<ref name=":1" />。

DKFZ的Timo Bund的工作組在2017年年底，透過識別牛肉牛乳因子的RNA以及其蛋白質產物，證明牛肉牛乳因子在人類細胞中可以長期存留<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Episomal-Persistierende DNA in Krebs- und chronischen Erkrankungen|url=https://www.dkfz.de/de/episomal-persistierende-DNA/index.php|url-status=no|access-date=2021-03-03|website=Deutsches Krebsforschungszentrum|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415172451/https://www.dkfz.de/de/episomal-persistierende-DNA/index.php}}</ref>。

2019年2月時，Ethel-Michele de Villiers在歐亞牛的血清和牛奶中找到新發現的[[病原体|病原体]]，可能會間接引發結腸癌的發展<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|date=2019|title=Risikofaktor für Darmkrebs in Milch entdeckt|trans-title=Colon cancer risk factor discovered in milk|url=https://www.springermedizin.de/risikofaktor-fuer-darmkrebs-in-milch-entdeckt/16599438|journal=CME|language=de|issue=4}}</ref>。

